`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- Converting from React Native `Modal` to an absolute-positioned `View` keeps TradeDialog in the same React tree as the rest of the HUD — making it composable with other overlays and avoiding the Z-index isolation that system modals impose on top of the game canvas.
- The backdrop `Pressable` needs its own `onPress={handleClose}` so tapping outside the card dismisses the trade UI, matching the FPS "look away / press Escape" pattern.
